sequenceDiagram
    participant Sarah as Sarah<br/>iPhone 15 Pro
    participant SE as Secure Element<br/>and Secure Enclave
    participant Terminal as Whole Foods<br/>NFC Terminal
    participant Acquirer as Acquirer<br/>Processor
    participant Visa as VisaNet<br/>plus VTS
    participant Chase as Chase Bank<br/>Issuer

    Note over Sarah,Chase: Sarah pays $47.50 at Whole Foods with Apple Pay

    Sarah->>SE: Double-click side button<br/>Wallet app opens
    Sarah->>SE: Face ID authentication
    SE->>SE: Secure Enclave verifies face<br/>Sends auth token to embedded SE

    Sarah->>Terminal: Holds iPhone near terminal
    Terminal->>SE: SELECT PPSE
    SE-->>Terminal: Available AIDs -- Visa
    Terminal->>SE: SELECT A0000000031010
    SE-->>Terminal: Visa applet selected
    Terminal->>SE: GET PROCESSING OPTIONS<br/>Amount: $47.50, Currency: USD
    SE->>SE: Generate ARQC cryptogram<br/>using DPAN key and ATC
    SE-->>Terminal: DPAN plus cryptogram<br/>Real PAN never transmitted

    Note over Sarah,Terminal: NFC complete in ~350ms -- phone can be removed

    Terminal->>Acquirer: ISO 8583 0100 auth request<br/>DPAN plus cryptogram
    Acquirer->>Visa: Route via token BIN range
    Visa->>Visa: VTS detokenizes DPAN to real PAN<br/>Validates cryptogram via HSM<br/>Checks domain restriction -- NFC
    Visa->>Chase: Auth request with real PAN<br/>$47.50 at Whole Foods

    Chase->>Chase: Account active -- yes<br/>Available credit -- sufficient<br/>Fraud score -- low risk
    Chase-->>Visa: Approved -- response code 00
    Visa->>Visa: Re-tokenize -- replace PAN with DPAN
    Visa-->>Acquirer: Approved response
    Acquirer-->>Terminal: Approved
    Terminal-->>Sarah: Checkmark and haptic feedback

    Note over Sarah,Chase: Total time: approximately 2 seconds
